SELECT s.supplier_name, COUNT(*) AS lead_time_count FROM Supplier s LEFT JOIN LeadTime lt ON s.supplier_id = lt.supplier_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name;
SELECT s.supplier_name, MAX(lt.lead_time_hours) AS max_lead_time FROM Supplier s LEFT JOIN LeadTime lt ON s.supplier_id = lt.supplier_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name;

SELECT s.supplier_name, o.order_date, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) AS total_cost FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder o ON s.supplier_id = o.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name, o.order_date;

SELECT s.supplier_name, COUNT(DISTINCT o.order_id) AS order_count, AVG(p.total_amount) AS avg_order_amount FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder p ON s.supplier_id = p.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON p.order_id = oi.order_id JOIN LeadTime lt ON p.order_id = lt.order_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name;

SELECT s.supplier_name, COUNT(DISTINCT o.order_id) AS order_count, MAX(lt.lead_time_hours) AS max_lead_time FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder p ON s.supplier_id = p.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON p.order_id = oi.order_id JOIN LeadTime lt ON p.order_id = lt.order_id WHERE p.status = 'In Progress' GROUP BY s.supplier_name;

SELECT s.supplier_name, o.order_id, COUNT(oi.item_id) AS num_items FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder o ON s.supplier_id = o.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name, o.order_id;

SELECT s.supplier_name, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) AS total_cost FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder o ON s.supplier_id = o.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id WHERE o.status = 'Delivered' GROUP BY s.supplier_name;
SELECT s.supplier_name, AVG(lt.lead_time_hours) AS avg_lead_time FROM Supplier s JOIN LeadTime lt ON s.supplier_id = lt.supplier_id GROUP BY s.supplier_name;

SELECT s1.supplier_name AS supplier_1, s2.supplier_name AS supplier_2, COUNT(*) AS order_count FROM Supplier s1 JOIN Supplier s2 ON s1.supplier_id < s2.supplier_id JOIN PurchaseOrder p1 ON s1.supplier_id = p1.supplier_id JOIN PurchaseOrder p2 ON s2.supplier_id = p2.supplier_id WHERE p1.status = p2.status GROUP BY s1.supplier_name, s2.supplier_name;

SELECT s.supplier_name, o.order_date, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) AS total_cost FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder o ON s.supplier_id = o.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id WHERE o.order_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY s.supplier_name, o.order_date;

SELECT s.supplier_name, AVG(p.total_amount) AS avg_order_amount FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder p ON s.supplier_id = p.supplier_id WHERE p.status = 'Delivered' GROUP BY s.supplier_name HAVING avg_order_amount > 1000;

SELECT s.supplier_name, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) AS total_cost FROM Supplier s JOIN PurchaseOrder o ON s.supplier_id = o.supplier_id JOIN OrderItem oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id WHERE o.status = 'Delivered' GROUP BY s.supplier_name HAVING total_cost > 5000;
